{"title":"西藏农民唱丰收","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":10,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏农民唱丰收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民主改革后的第一个丰收季节来到了西藏高原。这些日子里，到处都响彻着喜庆丰收，歌颂党的领导的欢乐歌声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方升起了红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尼木河两岸放金光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼满场粮满仓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收全靠共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不愁吃啊不愁穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮食满仓歌满山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互助合作办起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢欢喜喜庆丰年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“八字宪法”放红光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家户户粮满仓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积肥修渠大生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻身农奴喜洋洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国人民创造了这一件宝贝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多好的宝贝呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏农民拿着它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荒滩石山也开花。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}